# Bandit Level 1

## Goal
Find the password stored in a file called `readme` in the home directory.

## What I learned
- How to list files using `ls`
- How to read a file using `cat`
- What a home directory is

## My Approach

```bash
# First I listed the files to see what was there
ls

# Saw a file called readme — read it
cat readme
```

## The Result
The password was printed straight to the screen.

